---
title: Beef and Corn Chimichanga with Queso and Chopped Salad
description: Family favourite flavours in a loaded, cheesy chimichanga!  Top each bite with creamy queso and a refreshing chopped salad. Simple, convenient, and delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-and-corn-chimichanga-876003c5.jpg
